c=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d77b0f10356ec4a3cee54609ab67b933974b54","tid":1014414,"uid":151851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IONE mail</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好重要：你要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">買咗code先揀到人</span></span></strong>，而且<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">code買咗可以任轉成員</span></span></strong>，eg你今日想睇娜B，但係買得一個code同埋本身已經揀咗其他人，可以喺受信成員嗰到再設定娜B，所有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係信用卡嘅嘢都要預先入返錢，如果唔係佢會自動取消訂單</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\nmail嗰到其實android嗰邊，幾個方法裝app<br />\n<br />\n一係用我po出嚟嘅嗰個apk<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係直接用日本區AC down<br />\n<br />\n比錢嗰到，正路你裝完就咁會係港元顯示，不過好多時候㩒入去會變咗美金比錢，依個情況你個非日區AC就算有餘額都冇用，因為地區貨幣唔一樣<br />\n<br />\n解決：用tng（如果你冇信用卡），play會當你係信用卡照比<br />\n<br />\n如果本身有日區AC嘅就唔洗講咁多大家都識買卡/用信用卡/tng比錢<br />\n<br />\nIOS訂mail:<br />\n<br />\n1. 開個新日本apple acc，開acc果陣抄低安全問題，買日版itunes卡，入落日本apple acc 直接課金<br />\n記得係要日版itunes<br />\n<br />\n2. 開個新日本apple acc，開acc果陣抄低安全問題，down ione mail app，再轉個acc去香港，再send email去香港apple話自己用信用卡買唔到野，佢整一下就得，不過唔可以再用依個acc更新ione mail app，要再開一個新日本acc更新<br />\n<br />\n3. 開個新日本apple acc，開acc果陣抄低安全問題，用JCB卡直接課<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">介面</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3qLEyU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3qLEyU.jpg&h=40d92644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4qjJ1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4qjJ1y.jpg&h=db6123ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依個好重要，萬一有咩冬瓜豆腐你部機出咗事，你就係靠佢恢復本身嘅訂閱</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puacjAu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuacjAu.jpg&h=8957045d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">課金揀成員，如果你冇code，要喺粉紅色信封嗰到買</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1wyOvf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1wyOvf.jpg&h=a81e2a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMYpU9O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMYpU9O.png&h=1a64be52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你唔想再訂閱</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAndroid嘅話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FCNumWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFCNumWi.jpg&h=472b774a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0e7f593f54d6312f9e5403980d0d20401114feb","tid":1014414,"uid":151851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:32:30.000Z","msg":"船木巴嘅集體交收係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">17號3點開始喺mk地鐵站</span></span></strong>，如果17號唔得閒想另約交收<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 可以另外搵佢星期二打後放工時間</span></span></strong><br />\n地點就太子 or 觀塘 16號就炮台山<br />\n其他日子時間地點另傾<br />\n記得留埋訂個陣叫咩名同埋訂咗咩<br />\ntg：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa999651e3df867f6378aa6a911e07524e0e867f","tid":1014414,"uid":34992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MPjbUyD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMPjbUyD.gif